        "content": "<p>I would like to work on some simple results about fields to contribute to the math library. Results that seem achievable are: field extensions and their degree, splitting fields, the existence and uniqueness of finite fields, maybe some galois theory. Is anyone working in this direction? If so, what has already been done?</p>",
        "id": 150851783,
        "sender_full_name": "Joey van Langen",
        "timestamp": 1543934523
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>There is a branch <code>splitting_fields</code> on the community repo.</p>",
