        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1543934707
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also: welcome!</p>",
        "id": 150852027,
        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1543934717
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think that branch has a definition of the splitting field, but not yet the proofs of the interesting properties.</p>",
